20
00:03:09,731 --> 00:03:11,315
Yeah, but they're lying.

21
00:03:11,816 --> 00:03:12,941
I'm not.

22
00:03:19,157 --> 00:03:20,365
Are you sick?

23
00:03:21,034 --> 00:03:23,744
No-- Sure.

24
00:03:24,287 --> 00:03:26,538
You're not a very accomplished drunk.

25
00:03:27,624 --> 00:03:29,875
No, I'm always like this. lt's the...

26
00:03:30,627 --> 00:03:35,547
...motion sickness. When I was a kid,
I puked on my tricycle.

27
00:03:37,091 --> 00:03:38,717
I hate vehicles.

28
00:03:38,927 --> 00:03:40,510
Should I drive more slowly?

29
