It's cleaner on the inside.

32
00:04:15,421 --> 00:04:16,713
Please.

33
00:04:47,370 --> 00:04:50,330
Listen. Maybe this is a bad idea.

34
00:04:51,541 --> 00:04:53,166
It's too late.

35
