Hey, I bet you have a really neat
jukebox in here too someplace, huh?

41
00:05:19,193 --> 00:05:20,485
Over there maybe?

42
00:05:21,237 --> 00:05:22,446
No.

43
00:05:24,782 --> 00:05:27,034
No. This is the...

44
00:05:27,994 --> 00:05:32,122
...prototype of those.
It's the first one I had made.

45
00:05:32,749 --> 00:05:36,752
It works, but it's clunky.

46
00:05:49,307 --> 00:05:51,099
I call them telepods.

47
00:05:52,143 --> 00:05:53,852
They're controlled by this.

48
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:56,480
Thank God for that.

49
00:05:57,982 --> 00:06:01,068
So, what do they do,
the phone booths?

50
00:06:01,277 --> 00:06:02,319
Telepods.

51
00:06:06,991 --> 00:06:10,327
Okay, l need an object.

52
00:06:12,622 --> 00:06:15,082
