56
00:06:23,716 --> 00:06:25,050
No, I'm serious.

57
00:06:28,721 --> 00:06:31,473
Okay. Here it goes.

58
00:06:45,947 --> 00:06:47,656
Mm-hm.

59
00:06:50,451 --> 00:06:52,577
