79
00:09:14,053 --> 00:09:15,178
What happened?

80
00:09:15,388 --> 00:09:17,931
You get it all right,
you just can't handle it.

81
00:09:19,308 --> 00:09:23,103
Your stocking has just
been teleported...

82
00:09:23,479 --> 00:09:26,815
...from one pod to another.

83
00:09:27,024 --> 00:09:29,901
