and reintegrated there.

84
00:09:30,653 --> 00:09:31,736
Sort of.

85
00:09:32,905 --> 00:09:35,490
It'll change the world
as we know it, right?

86
00:09:39,328 --> 00:09:40,912
Oh. Oh.

87
00:09:43,499 --> 00:09:46,376
This is-- This is incredible.

88
00:09:46,586 --> 00:09:48,378
I mean, it's not possible, is it?

89
